you're married to?

20:13.722 --> 20:15.073
No, no, we'll do it.

20:15.107 --> 20:17.108
- Are you sure?
- Yes, we'll take them.

20:17.143 --> 20:19.060
We'll take both kids.

20:19.111 --> 20:20.695
There you are, Liz.

20:20.729 --> 20:22.280
I'm on my way up to see Jack,

20:22.314 --> 20:25.150
but as long as I'm still CEO,
I want to say two things.

20:25.184 --> 20:27.652
One, did you get a little sun?
You're glowing.

20:27.686 --> 20:31.022
And two, because of the lawsuit
and the P.R. nightmare

20:31.040 --> 20:33.158
and the den of sin you've built here,

20:33.192 --> 20:35.577
I have to go ahead and cancel <i>TGS.</i>

20:35.628 --> 20:38.630
Next Friday is your last show.

20:40.800 --> 20:42.250
Great news, Liz.

20:42.301 --> 20:44.202
Kenneth doesn't have
different hair anymore.

20:46.889 --> 20:49.507
Liz?
Liz?

20:52.423 --> 20:53.907
I showed up without a bra one day,

20:53.909 --> 20:56.759
